<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Document</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .main-wrapper {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      background-color: #e9e3e3;
      padding: 2rem 5rem;
    }

    .main-wrapper .container {
      background-color: #fff;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    .main-wrapper .header {
      background-color: #eef2ff;
      box-shadow: 0px 2px 8px 0px rgba(55, 48, 163, 0.08);
      padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
      margin: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      position: relative;
    }

    .main-wrapper .header h3 {
      margin: 0;
      margin-left: 0.2rem;
    }

    .main-wrapper .header a {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 0;
      margin-left: 1rem;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      color: #4f46e5;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 1.5rem 5rem 0 5rem;
    }

    .content h4 {
      margin: 0 0 0.2rem 0;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .content p {
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.5rem;
    }

    .applicant-wrapper {
      padding: 1.5rem 5rem;
      background-color: #fff;
    }

    .applicant>table {
      width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .applicant>table tr td:nth-last-child(1) {
      float: right;
    }

    .applicant .card {
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #eef2ff;
      box-shadow: 0px 4px 16px 0px rgba(49, 46, 129, 0.04);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }

    .applicant .card table {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .main-wrapper .footer {
      background: var(--Neutral-Grey-50, #f8fafc);
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .main-wrapper .footer p {
      word-break: break-all;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .main-wrapper .footer .Unsubscribe-wrapper span {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #475569;
      color: var(--Neutral-Grey-600, #475569);
    }

    .main-wrapper .footer .Unsubscribe-wrapper .border-height {
      height: 0.5rem;
      border-left: 1px solid #e0e7ff;
    }

    .main-wrapper .footer p {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      color: #64748b;
    }

    .main-wrapper .footer .social-mediaIcon-align tr td {
      padding: 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .main-wrapper .applicant a {
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* Extra small devices (phones, 600px and down) */
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {}

    /* Small devices (portrait tablets and large phones, 600px and up) */
    @media only screen and (min-width: 600px) {}

    /* Medium devices (landscape tablets, 768px and up) */
    @media only screen and (min-width: 768px) {}

    /* Large devices (laptops/desktops, 992px and up) */
    @media only screen and (min-width: 992px) {}

    /* Extra large devices (large laptops and desktops, 1200px and up) */
    @media only screen and (min-width: 1200px) {
      .main-wrapper {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        background-color: #e9e3e3;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="main-wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header applicant-section-hide">
        <table style="width: 100%">
          <tr>
            <td style="width: 20%">
              <a href="">
                <img
                  src="https://jobportal123.blob.core.windows.net/staticimages/portalLogo.png"
                  alt="LocationIcon" width="80px" />
              </a>
            </td>
            <td>
              <table align="center">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <table>
                      <tr>
                        <td>
                          <img
                            src="https://jobportal123.blob.core.windows.net/emailimages/profile-icon.png"
                            alt="profile-icon" />
                        </td>
                        <td>
                          <h3>Verify your email address</h3>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 20%"></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h4>Hi {{userName}} ðŸ‘‹,</h4>
        <h4>Your job is now live on <a href={{jobPortal}}>Job Portal</a>.</h4>
        <p>We have found the best matching candidates for your role.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="applicant-wrapper">
        <div class="applicant">
          <table>
            <tr>
              <td style="color: #312e81">
                <span style="margin-right: 0.3rem">{{jobTitle}}</span>
                <img
                  src="https://jobportal123.blob.core.windows.net/emailimages/angular1.png"
                  alt="" />
              </td>
              <td>
                <span
                  style="border-bottom: 1px solid black">{{jobApplicantsCount}}
                  Applicants</span>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
          <div class="card">
            <table>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <img
                    src="https://jobportal123.blob.core.windows.net/emailimages/profile.png"
                    alt="" />
                </td>
                <td>
                  <table>
                    <tr>
                      <td>
                        <span style="
                              margin-right: 0.3rem;
                              color: #0f172a;
                              font-weight: 700;
                            ">{{jobSeekerName}}</span>
                        <img
                          src="https://jobportal123.blob.core.windows.net/emailimages/angular1.png"
                          alt="angularIcon" />
                      </td>
                      <td style="
                            border-radius: 4px;
                            background: #f1f5f9;
                            padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem;
                            text-align: center;
                          ">
                        <span
                          style="color: #4f46e5">{{skillsMatchedPercent}}</span>
                        skills matched
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                  <p style="margin: 0; color: #64748b">
                    {{jobSeekerTitle}}
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
            <div style="
                  border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e7ff;
                  width: 100%;
                  margin: 0.8rem 0;
                "></div>
            <table style="color: #64748b">
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <img
                    src="https://jobportal123.blob.core.windows.net/emailimages/location.png"
                    alt="location" />
                  <span
                    style="margin-left: 0.4rem">{{jobSeekerLocations}}</span>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <img
                    src="https://jobportal123.blob.core.windows.net/emailimages/experience.png"
                    alt="experience" />
                  <span
                    style="margin-left: 0.4rem">{{jobSeekerExperience}}</span>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <img
                    src="https://jobportal123.blob.core.windows.net/emailimages/time.png"
                    alt="time" />
                  <span
                    style="margin-left: 0.4rem">{{jobSeekerNoticePeriod}}</span>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <img
                    src="https://jobportal123.blob.core.windows.net/emailimages/moneyLogo.png"
                    alt="moneyLogo" />
                  <span
                    style="margin-left: 0.4rem">{{jobSeekerCurrentSalary}}</span>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
            <div style="
                  border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e7ff;
                  width: 100%;
                  margin: 0.8rem 0;
                "></div>
            <table>
              <tr>
                <td style="
                      color: #0f172a;
                      font-weight: 700;
                      padding-right: 0.5rem;
                      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
                      position: relative;
                    ">
                  <span>Education</span>
                </td>
                <td style="color: #64748b; padding-bottom: 0.5rem">
                  {{jobSeekerEducation}}
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="
                      color: #0f172a;
                      font-weight: 700;
                      padding-right: 0.5rem;
                      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
                      position: relative;
                    ">
                  <span style="position: absolute; top: 0">Key Skills</span>
                </td>
                <td style="color: #64748b; padding-bottom: 0.5rem">
                  <p style="margin: 0">
                    {{jobSeekerKeySkills}}
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="applicant-section-hide">
            <table style="width: 100%">
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <a href={{applicantViewLink}} style="
                        color: white;
                        background-color: #4f46e5;
                        border-radius: 8px;
                        width: 80%;
                        display: inline-block;
                        padding: 0.5rem 0;
                        text-align: center;
                        border: none;
                        font-size: 1rem;
                      ">View</a>
                </td>
                <td style="text-align: center">
                  <a href={{resumeLink}} style="
                        color: black;
                        background-color: #eef2ff;
                        border-radius: 8px;
                        width: 80%;
                        display: inline-block;
                        padding: 0.5rem 0;
                        text-align: center;
                        border: none;
                        font-size: 1rem;
                      ">Download</a>
                </td>
                <td style="text-align: right">
                  <a href={{connectLink}} style="
                        color: black;
                        background-color: #eef2ff;
                        border-radius: 8px;
                        width: 80%;
                        display: inline-block;
                        padding: 0.5rem 0;
                        text-align: center;
                        border: none;
                        font-size: 1rem;
                      ">Contact</a>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer applicant-section-hide">
        <table align="center">
          <tr class="Unsubscribe-wrapper">
            <td><span>Unsubscribe</span></td>
            <td class="border-height">
              <div></div>
            </td>
            <td><span>Report a problem</span></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <p>
          You have received this mail because your e-mail ID is registered with
          jobportal.com. This is a system-generated e-mail, please don't reply
          to this message.
          Please do not pay any money to anyone who promises to find you a job.
          jobportal shall not have any
          responsibility in this regard. We recommend that you visit our Terms &
          Conditions and the
          Security Advice for more information.
        </p>
        <table align="center" class="social-mediaIcon-align">
          <tr>
            <td>
              <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/ratnaglobaltech">
                <img
                  src="https://jobportal123.blob.core.windows.net/emailimages/linkdine.png"
                  alt="linkedin" />
              </a>
            </td>
            <td>
              <a href="https://www.facebook.com/ratnaglobaltech">
                <img
                  src="https://jobportal123.blob.core.windows.net/emailimages/facebook.png"
                  alt="facebook" />
              </a>
            </td>
            <td>
              <a href="https://www.instagram.com/ratnaglobaltech">
                <img
                  src="https://jobportal123.blob.core.windows.net/emailimages/instagram.png"
                  alt="instagram" />
              </a>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>